law.history: Repealed 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 188, sec. 69, effective December 1, 1972. -- Amended 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 169, secs. 1 and 3; and ch. 174, sec. 5. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 1459, 1460, 1461, 1462.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Form of ballot -- Party emblems -- Method of indicating public questions.
